<L>__{exterior jim & pam's house laurel canyon day}
<A>__{pam and jim and the labrador sage trudge up a hill carrying the groceries to their modest little house tucked into a hill of dangling eucaplyptus trees. we sense a community of artists, hippies, volkswagens.}
