<D>__{it's only another $95,000 but i could get the best clothes. from india, morocco jim, clothes you can't find anywhere, we could get the richest people to come, miles davis, cher, the stones, it's gonna be the best boutique on la cienega jim... why are we walking, how come we don't have a car?}
